A lush, enchanted forest tunnel formed by thick green foliage and intertwining tree roots, with dappled sunlight filtering through the leaves. At the center of the tunnel stands a small, cute forest creature with big ears and a round shape, evoking a sense of wonder and whimsy. The setting is peaceful, magical, and reminiscent of Studio Ghibli animation style, especially from My Neighbor Totoro
